>&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com/how-to-migrate-a-website-to-another-server-using-updraft-migrator/">How to migrate a website to another server using Updraft Migrator</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href="http://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"wmullins";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:22535:"<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Building a website can be a complex and time consuming process that is usually comprised of 3 stages of production &#8211; </span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">Development, Staging and Production</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Each of these stages has its own URL to access the website; as such users need to be aware that when migrating a site through each stage, it is essential that the user makes sure everything is migrated correctly without any bugs. If anything goes wrong during one of these stages, it could result in a broken website.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As well as the development process of a new or redesigned website, many users also perform a migration when moving the site to another domain.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">A typical website migration involves the following tasks:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Move all files and folders</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Move the database</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Change all URLs in the database to match the new domain</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In this blog, we will walk you through how to easily migrate a website to another server using the</span><a href="https://updraftplus.com/shop/migrator"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">UpdraftPlus Migrator</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> feature. Using the Migrator add-on, a user can migrate or clone their website in a matter of minutes, with Migrator even taking care of replacing the serialised database. Users of Migrator will not need to deal with the hassle of FTP or CPanel when uploading files and folders as Migrator moves all of these in the background for you.</span></p>\n<p><b>Getting Started</b></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To get started, install a copy of the</span><a href="https://updraftplus.com/shop/migrator"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Migrator</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> add-on feature or upgrade to <a href="http://updraftplus.com/shop/updraftplus-premium/">UpdraftPlus Premium</a>, which represents the very best value as it includes the Migrator Add-On and 12 months of support, plus its Developer package comes with unlimited Add-On licences.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To explain how Migrator works, we are going to assume you have a development and staging server.¬†</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Assuming all development work is completed on your site, the next stage is migrating it to your staging server. First, ensure your staging server has a fresh copy of WordPress installed. Next, to perform the migration process, install and activate the</span><a href="https://updraftplus.com/shop/migrator"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">UpdraftPlus Migrator</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> feature on both the Development and Staging server.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Before proceeding any further, make sure you turn off any proxies between you and your site, such as Cloudflare, GoDaddy&#8217;s &#8220;Preview DNS&#8221; proxy or Opera Turbo/Road mode as these can potentially interfere with the clone process. Caching and minifying plugins are also a possible cause of migration problems. If possible, disable these before you create your backup ‚Äì or alternatively, turn them off if the migration stumbles.</span></p>\n<p><b>Migrate Website on Another Server Using Migrator</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">To start the migration process, login to your staging website.¬†</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Head over to Settings&gt;UpdraftPlus Backups&gt;Migrate / Clone.¬†</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Click on the &#8216;Receive a backup from a remote site&#8217; button in the Migrate section.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/9JFY3f-pCGnbXQIDWRkTAQUL63y-JbRgicpnf7hnC7DyI_DiVTscwUeNBJZvF2eKq0g3eIYgbDuP_IrleNinJHFmL86Ca6Ci1JKV4VTgVGGrmmINccRTFr2dgranC2cuNtISCQ4G.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-425092" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/9JFY3f-pCGnbXQIDWRkTAQUL63y-JbRgicpnf7hnC7DyI_DiVTscwUeNBJZvF2eKq0g3eIYgbDuP_IrleNinJHFmL86Ca6Ci1JKV4VTgVGGrmmINccRTFr2dgranC2cuNtISCQ4G.png" alt="" width="1047" height="277" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/9JFY3f-pCGnbXQIDWRkTAQUL63y-JbRgicpnf7hnC7DyI_DiVTscwUeNBJZvF2eKq0g3eIYgbDuP_IrleNinJHFmL86Ca6Ci1JKV4VTgVGGrmmINccRTFr2dgranC2cuNtISCQ4G.png 1047w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/9JFY3f-pCGnbXQIDWRkTAQUL63y-JbRgicpnf7hnC7DyI_DiVTscwUeNBJZvF2eKq0g3eIYgbDuP_IrleNinJHFmL86Ca6Ci1JKV4VTgVGGrmmINccRTFr2dgranC2cuNtISCQ4G-300x79.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/9JFY3f-pCGnbXQIDWRkTAQUL63y-JbRgicpnf7hnC7DyI_DiVTscwUeNBJZvF2eKq0g3eIYgbDuP_IrleNinJHFmL86Ca6Ci1JKV4VTgVGGrmmINccRTFr2dgranC2cuNtISCQ4G-768x203.png 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/9JFY3f-pCGnbXQIDWRkTAQUL63y-JbRgicpnf7hnC7DyI_DiVTscwUeNBJZvF2eKq0g3eIYgbDuP_IrleNinJHFmL86Ca6Ci1JKV4VTgVGGrmmINccRTFr2dgranC2cuNtISCQ4G-1024x271.png 1024w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/9JFY3f-pCGnbXQIDWRkTAQUL63y-JbRgicpnf7hnC7DyI_DiVTscwUeNBJZvF2eKq0g3eIYgbDuP_IrleNinJHFmL86Ca6Ci1JKV4VTgVGGrmmINccRTFr2dgranC2cuNtISCQ4G-510x135.png 510w" sizes="(max-width: 1047px) 100vw, 1047px" /></a></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This will open settings. Click on the &#8216;Create Key&#8217; button.</span></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/9JFY3f-pCGnbXQIDWRkTAQUL63y-JbRgicpnf7hnC7DyI_DiVTscwUeNBJZvF2eKq0g3eIYgbDuP_IrleNinJHFmL86Ca6Ci1JKV4VTgVGGrmmINccRTFr2dgranC2cuNtISCQ4G-1.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-425093" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/9JFY3f-pCGnbXQIDWRkTAQUL63y-JbRgicpnf7hnC7DyI_DiVTscwUeNBJZvF2eKq0g3eIYgbDuP_IrleNinJHFmL86Ca6Ci1JKV4VTgVGGrmmINccRTFr2dgranC2cuNtISCQ4G-1.png" alt="" width="1047" height="277" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/9JFY3f-pCGnbXQIDWRkTAQUL63y-JbRgicpnf7hnC7DyI_DiVTscwUeNBJZvF2eKq0g3eIYgbDuP_IrleNinJHFmL86Ca6Ci1JKV4VTgVGGrmmINccRTFr2dgranC2cuNtISCQ4G-1.png 1047w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/9JFY3f-pCGnbXQIDWRkTAQUL63y-JbRgicpnf7hnC7DyI_DiVTscwUeNBJZvF2eKq0g3eIYgbDuP_IrleNinJHFmL86Ca6Ci1JKV4VTgVGGrmmINccRTFr2dgranC2cuNtISCQ4G-1-300x79.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/9JFY3f-pCGnbXQIDWRkTAQUL63y-JbRgicpnf7hnC7DyI_DiVTscwUeNBJZvF2eKq0g3eIYgbDuP_IrleNinJHFmL86Ca6Ci1JKV4VTgVGGrmmINccRTFr2dgranC2cuNtISCQ4G-1-768x203.png 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/9JFY3f-pCGnbXQIDWRkTAQUL63y-JbRgicpnf7hnC7DyI_DiVTscwUeNBJZvF2eKq0g3eIYgbDuP_IrleNinJHFmL86Ca6Ci1JKV4VTgVGGrmmINccRTFr2dgranC2cuNtISCQ4G-1-1024x271.png 1024w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/9JFY3f-pCGnbXQIDWRkTAQUL63y-JbRgicpnf7hnC7DyI_DiVTscwUeNBJZvF2eKq0g3eIYgbDuP_IrleNinJHFmL86Ca6Ci1JKV4VTgVGGrmmINccRTFr2dgranC2cuNtISCQ4G-1-510x135.png 510w" sizes="(max-width: 1047px) 100vw, 1047px" /></a></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Copy the generated key. You will need this for the next few steps. The key acts as a bridge for transporting data from source to destination site.</span></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/JoJAxSk_tZrHE7BD4gVottmSjE7wbYPKe4VdLIlcfU79JHwWLYAWRJ3tQ2nGYAYHKZC9g4FpH6dmfQctMVLgMA_DsfCs1x-OIL-CtNnlxHnSlqR2T6gfGxFh2cBWoQwua1PzngX1.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-425094" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/JoJAxSk_tZrHE7BD4gVottmSjE7wbYPKe4VdLIlcfU79JHwWLYAWRJ3tQ2nGYAYHKZC9g4FpH6dmfQctMVLgMA_DsfCs1x-OIL-CtNnlxHnSlqR2T6gfGxFh2cBWoQwua1PzngX1.png" alt="" width="963" height="409" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/JoJAxSk_tZrHE7BD4gVottmSjE7wbYPKe4VdLIlcfU79JHwWLYAWRJ3tQ2nGYAYHKZC9g4FpH6dmfQctMVLgMA_DsfCs1x-OIL-CtNnlxHnSlqR2T6gfGxFh2cBWoQwua1PzngX1.png 963w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/JoJAxSk_tZrHE7BD4gVottmSjE7wbYPKe4VdLIlcfU79JHwWLYAWRJ3tQ2nGYAYHKZC9g4FpH6dmfQctMVLgMA_DsfCs1x-OIL-CtNnlxHnSlqR2T6gfGxFh2cBWoQwua1PzngX1-300x127.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/JoJAxSk_tZrHE7BD4gVottmSjE7wbYPKe4VdLIlcfU79JHwWLYAWRJ3tQ2nGYAYHKZC9g4FpH6dmfQctMVLgMA_DsfCs1x-OIL-CtNnlxHnSlqR2T6gfGxFh2cBWoQwua1PzngX1-768x326.png 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/JoJAxSk_tZrHE7BD4gVottmSjE7wbYPKe4VdLIlcfU79JHwWLYAWRJ3tQ2nGYAYHKZC9g4FpH6dmfQctMVLgMA_DsfCs1x-OIL-CtNnlxHnSlqR2T6gfGxFh2cBWoQwua1PzngX1-510x217.png 510w" sizes="(max-width: 963px) 100vw, 963px" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Next, login to your development site.¬†</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Go to Settings&gt;UpdraftPlus Backups&gt;Migrate / Clone.¬†</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">From the Migrate section, click on the button &#8216;Send a backup to another site&#8217;.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-425095" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed.png" alt="" width="696" height="193" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed.png 512w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed-300x83.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed-510x141.png 510w" sizes="(max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px" /></a></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Click on the &#8216;Add a site&#8217; link and add the generated site key that was created in the previous steps in the ‚ÄòSite Key‚Äô box and then press ‚ÄòAdd site‚Äô.</span></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed-1.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-425096" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed-1.png" alt="" width="706" height="215" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed-1.png 512w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed-1-300x91.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed-1-510x155.png 510w" sizes="(max-width: 706px) 100vw, 706px" /></a></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">After adding a key you should now see the destination site URL. This means you are ready to migrate from development to staging server. Click the &#8216;Send&#8217; button.</span></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/nH4fIgQE-PK6WaKrI5e0-eg9_mWmG2tWpTMlatQPdjRsRxC20jrbB-PAHv838X5eBf6Y8BO_fNiwM2pM5hLRDPf-YWeOJOg4KoFyVEn0J7ciqbhOHLD6lIXWLa50zdyWvFQFjMlQ.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-425097" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/nH4fIgQE-PK6WaKrI5e0-eg9_mWmG2tWpTMlatQPdjRsRxC20jrbB-PAHv838X5eBf6Y8BO_fNiwM2pM5hLRDPf-YWeOJOg4KoFyVEn0J7ciqbhOHLD6lIXWLa50zdyWvFQFjMlQ.png" alt="" width="1232" height="362" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/nH4fIgQE-PK6WaKrI5e0-eg9_mWmG2tWpTMlatQPdjRsRxC20jrbB-PAHv838X5eBf6Y8BO_fNiwM2pM5hLRDPf-YWeOJOg4KoFyVEn0J7ciqbhOHLD6lIXWLa50zdyWvFQFjMlQ.png 1232w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/nH4fIgQE-PK6WaKrI5e0-eg9_mWmG2tWpTMlatQPdjRsRxC20jrbB-PAHv838X5eBf6Y8BO_fNiwM2pM5hLRDPf-YWeOJOg4KoFyVEn0J7ciqbhOHLD6lIXWLa50zdyWvFQFjMlQ-300x88.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/nH4fIgQE-PK6WaKrI5e0-eg9_mWmG2tWpTMlatQPdjRsRxC20jrbB-PAHv838X5eBf6Y8BO_fNiwM2pM5hLRDPf-YWeOJOg4KoFyVEn0J7ciqbhOHLD6lIXWLa50zdyWvFQFjMlQ-768x226.png 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/nH4fIgQE-PK6WaKrI5e0-eg9_mWmG2tWpTMlatQPdjRsRxC20jrbB-PAHv838X5eBf6Y8BO_fNiwM2pM5hLRDPf-YWeOJOg4KoFyVEn0J7ciqbhOHLD6lIXWLa50zdyWvFQFjMlQ-1024x301.png 1024w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/nH4fIgQE-PK6WaKrI5e0-eg9_mWmG2tWpTMlatQPdjRsRxC20jrbB-PAHv838X5eBf6Y8BO_fNiwM2pM5hLRDPf-YWeOJOg4KoFyVEn0J7ciqbhOHLD6lIXWLa50zdyWvFQFjMlQ-1080x317.png 1080w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/nH4fIgQE-PK6WaKrI5e0-eg9_mWmG2tWpTMlatQPdjRsRxC20jrbB-PAHv838X5eBf6Y8BO_fNiwM2pM5hLRDPf-YWeOJOg4KoFyVEn0J7ciqbhOHLD6lIXWLa50zdyWvFQFjMlQ-510x150.png 510w" sizes="(max-width: 1232px) 100vw, 1232px" /></a></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">After clicking on the Send button, you will be asked to select the options that you want to clone. Choose all options except &#8216;WordPress core&#8217;, as you have already installed WordPress on the destination site.</span></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/z_7RoUrzxhuMlWD-o4RpvqWaThZSZ0IUJe9X6pzreNoDTaXKa3EPpzihRmPAaFOe-Wg80sRwiyXrM6E86G7bgZogNxkEE2a04lvUIa7b1XH1dnLzIqx8fsAOP_RavBGr_Dt5Wdd.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-425098" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/z_7RoUrzxhuMlWD-o4RpvqWaThZSZ0IUJe9X6pzreNoDTaXKa3EPpzihRmPAaFOe-Wg80sRwiyXrM6E86G7bgZogNxkEE2a04lvUIa7b1XH1dnLzIqx8fsAOP_RavBGr_Dt5Wdd.png" alt="" width="754" height="462" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/z_7RoUrzxhuMlWD-o4RpvqWaThZSZ0IUJe9X6pzreNoDTaXKa3EPpzihRmPAaFOe-Wg80sRwiyXrM6E86G7bgZogNxkEE2a04lvUIa7b1XH1dnLzIqx8fsAOP_RavBGr_Dt5Wdd.png 754w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/z_7RoUrzxhuMlWD-o4RpvqWaThZSZ0IUJe9X6pzreNoDTaXKa3EPpzihRmPAaFOe-Wg80sRwiyXrM6E86G7bgZogNxkEE2a04lvUIa7b1XH1dnLzIqx8fsAOP_RavBGr_Dt5Wdd-300x184.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/z_7RoUrzxhuMlWD-o4RpvqWaThZSZ0IUJe9X6pzreNoDTaXKa3EPpzihRmPAaFOe-Wg80sRwiyXrM6E86G7bgZogNxkEE2a04lvUIa7b1XH1dnLzIqx8fsAOP_RavBGr_Dt5Wdd-510x312.png 510w" sizes="(max-width: 754px) 100vw, 754px" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Once you have ticked all the options required, click the &#8216;Send&#8217; button.¬†</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">UpdraftPlus will now start the process of migrating your site to the destination site. This could take some time depending on the size of your website.¬†</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">After completion of the process, you should see a new backup visible in &#8216;Existing Backups&#8217;.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/8lYSRGGAgpSerMjVPuJNApuOuC8Ytlv_Tj5LfQPOtb_9lIPDrNd3Iq9mlguRg5QuOTVYrvTGSFLUkGcKm068xUgq5b17uAmSqSJfnpFlm5-10ZaajmI2xhMMU3lruH_c8fWu2dga.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-425099" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/8lYSRGGAgpSerMjVPuJNApuOuC8Ytlv_Tj5LfQPOtb_9lIPDrNd3Iq9mlguRg5QuOTVYrvTGSFLUkGcKm068xUgq5b17uAmSqSJfnpFlm5-10ZaajmI2xhMMU3lruH_c8fWu2dga.png" alt="" width="1600" height="272" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/8lYSRGGAgpSerMjVPuJNApuOuC8Ytlv_Tj5LfQPOtb_9lIPDrNd3Iq9mlguRg5QuOTVYrvTGSFLUkGcKm068xUgq5b17uAmSqSJfnpFlm5-10ZaajmI2xhMMU3lruH_c8fWu2dga.png 1600w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/8lYSRGGAgpSerMjVPuJNApuOuC8Ytlv_Tj5LfQPOtb_9lIPDrNd3Iq9mlguRg5QuOTVYrvTGSFLUkGcKm068xUgq5b17uAmSqSJfnpFlm5-10ZaajmI2xhMMU3lruH_c8fWu2dga-300x51.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/8lYSRGGAgpSerMjVPuJNApuOuC8Ytlv_Tj5LfQPOtb_9lIPDrNd3Iq9mlguRg5QuOTVYrvTGSFLUkGcKm068xUgq5b17uAmSqSJfnpFlm5-10ZaajmI2xhMMU3lruH_c8fWu2dga-768x131.png 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/8lYSRGGAgpSerMjVPuJNApuOuC8Ytlv_Tj5LfQPOtb_9lIPDrNd3Iq9mlguRg5QuOTVYrvTGSFLUkGcKm068xUgq5b17uAmSqSJfnpFlm5-10ZaajmI2xhMMU3lruH_c8fWu2dga-1024x174.png 1024w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/8lYSRGGAgpSerMjVPuJNApuOuC8Ytlv_Tj5LfQPOtb_9lIPDrNd3Iq9mlguRg5QuOTVYrvTGSFLUkGcKm068xUgq5b17uAmSqSJfnpFlm5-10ZaajmI2xhMMU3lruH_c8fWu2dga-1080x184.png 1080w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/8lYSRGGAgpSerMjVPuJNApuOuC8Ytlv_Tj5LfQPOtb_9lIPDrNd3Iq9mlguRg5QuOTVYrvTGSFLUkGcKm068xUgq5b17uAmSqSJfnpFlm5-10ZaajmI2xhMMU3lruH_c8fWu2dga-510x87.png 510w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /></a></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This new backup indicates that the source site has successfully sent a backup set to the destination site.</span></p>\n<p><b>Restore the backup on the destination site</b></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Once you have completed the above steps in the destination site, Click the &#8216;Restore&#8217; button and then select all options.</span></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/GIQih3oWjzMIg05vNFlCwSQMyW1aTHUyAk56DvIaKVWOFgmqZEsMQTsE6FM12bbN0o3ts_zeX17L_-0-0xOM60vVogqtgBqVR8FcLqcp0M7cWJL9_fcl4HSYZSb10CrSgBcNdYbF.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-425100" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/GIQih3oWjzMIg05vNFlCwSQMyW1aTHUyAk56DvIaKVWOFgmqZEsMQTsE6FM12bbN0o3ts_zeX17L_-0-0xOM60vVogqtgBqVR8FcLqcp0M7cWJL9_fcl4HSYZSb10CrSgBcNdYbF.png" alt="" width="1600" height="263" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/GIQih3oWjzMIg05vNFlCwSQMyW1aTHUyAk56DvIaKVWOFgmqZEsMQTsE6FM12bbN0o3ts_zeX17L_-0-0xOM60vVogqtgBqVR8FcLqcp0M7cWJL9_fcl4HSYZSb10CrSgBcNdYbF.png 1600w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/GIQih3oWjzMIg05vNFlCwSQMyW1aTHUyAk56DvIaKVWOFgmqZEsMQTsE6FM12bbN0o3ts_zeX17L_-0-0xOM60vVogqtgBqVR8FcLqcp0M7cWJL9_fcl4HSYZSb10CrSgBcNdYbF-300x49.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/GIQih3oWjzMIg05vNFlCwSQMyW1aTHUyAk56DvIaKVWOFgmqZEsMQTsE6FM12bbN0o3ts_zeX17L_-0-0xOM60vVogqtgBqVR8FcLqcp0M7cWJL9_fcl4HSYZSb10CrSgBcNdYbF-768x126.png 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/GIQih3oWjzMIg05vNFlCwSQMyW1aTHUyAk56DvIaKVWOFgmqZEsMQTsE6FM12bbN0o3ts_zeX17L_-0-0xOM60vVogqtgBqVR8FcLqcp0M7cWJL9_fcl4HSYZSb10CrSgBcNdYbF-1024x168.png 1024w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/GIQih3oWjzMIg05vNFlCwSQMyW1aTHUyAk56DvIaKVWOFgmqZEsMQTsE6FM12bbN0o3ts_zeX17L_-0-0xOM60vVogqtgBqVR8FcLqcp0M7cWJL9_fcl4HSYZSb10CrSgBcNdYbF-1080x178.png 1080w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/GIQih3oWjzMIg05vNFlCwSQMyW1aTHUyAk56DvIaKVWOFgmqZEsMQTsE6FM12bbN0o3ts_zeX17L_-0-0xOM60vVogqtgBqVR8FcLqcp0M7cWJL9_fcl4HSYZSb10CrSgBcNdYbF-510x84.png 510w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /></a></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Yc31Ce6Oe6TCBG1-RYmw8RThNGqL6FlaURYYYuYUs5d_P-vzFIWy_0ws6eCwCBGAwX-8d77v-jPo6zZRFJ8g_xqTF2x3iu_2pE-HASuO64h6cyqy0ToHd03czRV1f-FrGtGpceUJ.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-425103" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Yc31Ce6Oe6TCBG1-RYmw8RThNGqL6FlaURYYYuYUs5d_P-vzFIWy_0ws6eCwCBGAwX-8d77v-jPo6zZRFJ8g_xqTF2x3iu_2pE-HASuO64h6cyqy0ToHd03czRV1f-FrGtGpceUJ.png" alt="" width="778" height="690" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Yc31Ce6Oe6TCBG1-RYmw8RThNGqL6FlaURYYYuYUs5d_P-vzFIWy_0ws6eCwCBGAwX-8d77v-jPo6zZRFJ8g_xqTF2x3iu_2pE-HASuO64h6cyqy0ToHd03czRV1f-FrGtGpceUJ.png 778w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Yc31Ce6Oe6TCBG1-RYmw8RThNGqL6FlaURYYYuYUs5d_P-vzFIWy_0ws6eCwCBGAwX-8d77v-jPo6zZRFJ8g_xqTF2x3iu_2pE-HASuO64h6cyqy0ToHd03czRV1f-FrGtGpceUJ-300x266.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Yc31Ce6Oe6TCBG1-RYmw8RThNGqL6FlaURYYYuYUs5d_P-vzFIWy_0ws6eCwCBGAwX-8d77v-jPo6zZRFJ8g_xqTF2x3iu_2pE-HASuO64h6cyqy0ToHd03czRV1f-FrGtGpceUJ-768x681.png 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Yc31Ce6Oe6TCBG1-RYmw8RThNGqL6FlaURYYYuYUs5d_P-vzFIWy_0ws6eCwCBGAwX-8d77v-jPo6zZRFJ8g_xqTF2x3iu_2pE-HASuO64h6cyqy0ToHd03czRV1f-FrGtGpceUJ-510x452.png 510w" sizes="(max-width: 778px) 100vw, 778px" /></a></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Next, you will see a checkbox for database restoration options. Tick the checkbox and continue the process. As we are restoring the database of the source site, we need to update the URLs with the new site URLs.</span></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/722myXesJ5RSD8DTYHtvmSkpXSofsXvk6YU8A9RPGkwBbMl327QEFkKkto-6mD9o3EI51SKTkL2VD_cd6gC77WcSis7H9CKhEvBWILlqT0xtEEtwIzLApSocFtc6fF2R6Q2OM7_6.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-425104" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/722myXesJ5RSD8DTYHtvmSkpXSofsXvk6YU8A9RPGkwBbMl327QEFkKkto-6mD9o3EI51SKTkL2VD_cd6gC77WcSis7H9CKhEvBWILlqT0xtEEtwIzLApSocFtc6fF2R6Q2OM7_6.png" alt="" width="774" height="678" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/722myXesJ5RSD8DTYHtvmSkpXSofsXvk6YU8A9RPGkwBbMl327QEFkKkto-6mD9o3EI51SKTkL2VD_cd6gC77WcSis7H9CKhEvBWILlqT0xtEEtwIzLApSocFtc6fF2R6Q2OM7_6.png 774w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/722myXesJ5RSD8DTYHtvmSkpXSofsXvk6YU8A9RPGkwBbMl327QEFkKkto-6mD9o3EI51SKTkL2VD_cd6gC77WcSis7H9CKhEvBWILlqT0xtEEtwIzLApSocFtc6fF2R6Q2OM7_6-300x263.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/722myXesJ5RSD8DTYHtvmSkpXSofsXvk6YU8A9RPGkwBbMl327QEFkKkto-6mD9o3EI51SKTkL2VD_cd6gC77WcSis7H9CKhEvBWILlqT0xtEEtwIzLApSocFtc6fF2R6Q2OM7_6-768x673.png 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/722myXesJ5RSD8DTYHtvmSkpXSofsXvk6YU8A9RPGkwBbMl327QEFkKkto-6mD9o3EI51SKTkL2VD_cd6gC77WcSis7H9CKhEvBWILlqT0xtEEtwIzLApSocFtc6fF2R6Q2OM7_6-510x447.png 510w" sizes="(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px" /></a></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Wait for UpdraftPlus to finish the process of migration. Once complete, log out of the dashboard and login again. You should see now your site is migrated successfully.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">That‚Äôs it! It‚Äôs really that simple to migrate a website from one server to another using Migrator.¬†</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Get Migrator by upgrading to <a href="http://updraftplus.com/shop/updraftplus-premium/">UpdraftPlus Premium</a> or by adding the</span><a href="https://updraftplus.com/shop/migrator"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Migrator</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> feature today.</span></p>\n<p>By Sajid Sayyad</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com/how-to-migrate-a-website-to-another-server-using-updraft-migrator/">How to migrate a website to another server using Updraft Migrator</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href="http://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:95:"https://updraftplus.com/how-to-migrate-a-website-to-another-server-using-updraft-migrator/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:90:"https://updraftplus.com/how-to-migrate-a-website-to-another-server-using-updraft-migrator/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:64:"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:63:"Duplicate a slideshow and add custom CSS with MetaSlider 3.14.0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:58:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/rhCx3iTNM4A/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:96:"https://updraftplus.com/duplicate-a-slideshow-and-add-custom-css-with-metaslider-3-14-0/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Mon, 05 Aug 2019 11:12:38 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:10:"MetaSlider";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:17:"MetaSlider update";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:33:"https://updraftplus.com/?p=419149";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:811:"<p>As part of our drive to continually improve MetaSlider &#8211; the most popular WordPress slider plugin &#8211; we have launched the first stage of a series of updates that will contribute an overall improvement of MetaSlider, with newly added features &#8230; <a href="https://updraftplus.com/duplicate-a-slideshow-and-add-custom-css-with-metaslider-3-14-0/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com/duplicate-a-slideshow-and-add-custom-css-with-metaslider-3-14-0/">Duplicate a slideshow and add custom CSS with MetaSlider 3.14.0</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href="http://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"wmullins";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3532:"<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As part of our drive to continually improve MetaSlider &#8211; the most popular WordPress slider plugin &#8211; we have launched the first stage of a series of updates that will contribute an overall improvement of MetaSlider, with newly added features and an updated UI.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">When using the latest version of MetaSlider, users can now </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">quickly duplicate a slideshow and copy over all settings. This is useful if you want a starting point for another slideshow with the same settings if you want to have similar slideshows on mobile, but with a few differences.</span></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/toolbar.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-419150" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/toolbar.png" alt="" width="2688" height="884" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/toolbar.png 2688w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/toolbar-300x99.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/toolbar-768x253.png 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/toolbar-1024x337.png 1024w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/toolbar-1080x355.png 1080w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/toolbar-510x168.png 510w" sizes="(max-width: 2688px) 100vw, 2688px" /></a></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Other new features for this new release also include:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Add custom CSS to a specific slideshow to to customize the appearance</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Use recipes/code snippets to quickly add common CSS rules</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Add CSS styles that change the behavior of any page that the slideshow is on. For example, if you want the header to be full width you can now add a style to take care of that</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We recommend the update for all users. The full change-log is as follows</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">FEATURE: Adds ability to duplicate a slideshow</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">FEATURE: Adds toolbar with various utilities</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">FEATURE: Adds unified notification system</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">REFACTOR: Moves inline styles out of the body tag</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">REFACTOR: Refactors the preview module to be called from anywhere</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">REFACTOR: Refactors the way slides and the slideshow saving works</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">REFACTOR: Refactors the shortcode copy module</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">REFACTOR: Adds helper functions to better manage the routes files</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">FIX: Fixes bug where adding a class name via Gutenberg crashes the block</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com/duplicate-a-slideshow-and-add-custom-css-with-metaslider-3-14-0/">Duplicate a slideshow and add custom CSS with MetaSlider 3.14.0</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href="http://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:93:"https://updraftplus.com/duplicate-a-slideshow-and-add-custom-css-with-metaslider-3-14-0/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:88:"https://updraftplus.com/duplicate-a-slideshow-and-add-custom-css-with-metaslider-3-14-0/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:70:"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"UpdraftPlus Vault expands backup regions across the world";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:58:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/Pkd9oPeSr0A/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:90:"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-vault-expands-backup-regions-across-the-world/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Mon, 29 Jul 2019 08:22:15 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:28:"UpdraftPlus development news";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:17:"updraftplus vault";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"UpdraftVault";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5:"vault";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:33:"https://updraftplus.com/?p=416541";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:796:"<p>As part of our continued effort to improve all of our services, we have recently completed an update for our popular UpdraftPlus Vault product.¬† UpdraftPlus Vault is a built-in storage space option for your UpdraftPlus backups. Using Vault gives numerous &#8230; <a href="https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-vault-expands-backup-regions-across-the-world/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-vault-expands-backup-regions-across-the-world/">UpdraftPlus Vault expands backup regions across the world</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href="http://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"wmullins";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3196:"<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As part of our continued effort to improve all of our services, we have recently completed an update for our popular </span><a href="https://updraftplus.com/updraftvault/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">UpdraftPlus Vault</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> product.¬†</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">UpdraftPlus Vault is a built-in storage space option for your UpdraftPlus backups. Using Vault gives numerous benefits including dedicated compatibility with <a href="https://updraftplus.com/">UpdraftPlus</a>, which means you do not have to depend on a third party storage system and all the complications that come with figuring out what suitable product to buy and how to connect it to your backups. As UpdraftPlus Vault has been tailored specifically for use in UpdraftPlus, it is incredibly simple to set up, understand and use.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">UpdraftPlus Vault works by storing multiple copies of your backups at data-centres in various parts of the world. As part of this update, we have now added 11 new regions for UpdraftPlus Vault storage. This means that your data will now be stored at the nearest region to you.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Although we cannot guarantee the precise location of your data, UpdraftPlus Vault will now prioritise data centres within your continent.</span></p>\n<p><strong>The original regions were:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">US West (Oregon)</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">EU (Ireland)</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Asia Pacific (Singapore)</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Asia Pacific (Sydney)</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">South America (S√£o Paulo)</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>The new regions are:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">US East (N. Virginia)</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">US East (Ohio)</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">US West (N. California)</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Canada (Central)</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Asia Pacific (Mumbai)</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Asia Pacific (Seoul)</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Asia Pacific (Tokyo)</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">EU (Frankfurt)</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">EU (Paris)</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">EU (London)</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">EU (Stockholm)</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We are sure that this update will help improve your UpdraftPlus Vault experience. If you have any questions or comments, be sure to share them with us in the comments section below.¬†</span></p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-vault-expands-backup-regions-across-the-world/">UpdraftPlus Vault expands backup regions across the world</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href="http://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:87:"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-vault-expands-backup-regions-across-the-world/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:82:"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-vault-expands-backup-regions-across-the-world/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:76:"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:91:"WP-Optimize expands to a market leading 3-in-1 optimization plugin with new caching feature";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:58:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/40fqevlBXg4/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:124:"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-expands-to-a-market-leading-3-in-1-optimization-plugin-with-new-caching-feature/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Thu, 25 Jul 2019 09:34:33 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"WP Optimize";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"WP-O";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"WP-Optimise";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:18:"WP-Optimise Update";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"WP-Optimize";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:17:"WP-Optmize update";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:33:"https://updraftplus.com/?p=415219";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:885:"<p>After a lot of development and hard work that has included our recent image optimization feature, we are excited to share with WP-Optimize users the latest breaking news; The all new caching feature has now been released! This new development &#8230; <a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-expands-to-a-market-leading-3-in-1-optimization-plugin-with-new-caching-feature/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-expands-to-a-market-leading-3-in-1-optimization-plugin-with-new-caching-feature/">WP-Optimize expands to a market leading 3-in-1 optimization plugin with new caching feature</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href="http://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"wmullins";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:10043:"<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">After a lot of development and hard work that has included our recent </span><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-announce-release-of-new-leading-image-compression-feature/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">image optimization</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> feature, we are excited to share with </span><a href="https://getwpo.com/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">WP-Optimize</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> users the latest breaking news; The all new caching feature has now been released! This new development makes WP-Optimize a market leading 3-in-1 plugin that now combines </span><b>caching, database cleaning and image optimization</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> that now all work together to help make your site run faster. WP-Optimize caching has been a highly requested feature that we have now available to both our free and premium users..¬†</span></p>\n<p><b>How does caching work?</b></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Caching makes the most of your WordPress posts and pages by loading them as static files. When these static files are viewed by users, it reduces the amount of processing load on the web server and overload if PHP and MySQL are used. This can help improve the performance of the site and is a sure-fire way to ensure that web pages load at lightning-fast speeds.</span></p>\n<p><b>How to use the WP-Optimize caching feature</b></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Video walk-thru: While written instructions on how caching work can be helpful, for many users a simple walk-thru video can be a lot easier and quicker to process and understand. So be sure to check out the following video we made that takes you through the process of how to use cache.¬†</span></p>\n<p><iframe title="How to use WP-Optimize cache" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/337247770?dnt=1&#038;app_id=122963" width="1080" height="608" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><strong><br />\nSetting up caching:</strong></p>\n<p>With WP-Optimize caching, we have specially designed the feature to give a wide range of options to the user. However, if you are the kind of person just wants to turn something on and let it run, just toggle the ‚Äúenable page caching‚Äù button and we will automatically optimize all the different caching tasks for you. This feature enables users with all levels of knowledge to access the full advantages of caching.</p>\n<div id="attachment_415229" style="width: 519px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-72.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-415229" class="wp-image-415229 size-full" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-72.jpg" alt="" width="509" height="335" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-72.jpg 509w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-72-300x197.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 509px) 100vw, 509px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-415229" class="wp-caption-text">How the caching settings appear in the plugin</p></div>\n<p>If you prefer to do things yourself and dig into the finer details, you can manually setup your sites caching options yourself.</p>\n<p><b>Mobile and logged in users cache</b></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you prefer to setup the cache yourself, there are options within the plugin that will let you manually set ‚Äúmobile‚Äù and ‚Äúlogged in users‚Äù cache. Mobile cache enables users who access your site via a mobile or tablet to get a device specific cached version, while ‚Äúlogged in users cache‚Äù enables secured cached content for all of your logged in users. If you want to enable this option, just toggle the buttons to the on position. The options are just the first in an amazing long list of features that will make your site faster.¬†¬†¬†</span></p>\n<div id="attachment_415249" style="width: 555px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-78.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-415249" class="wp-image-415249 " src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-78.jpg" alt="" width="545" height="224" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-78.jpg 579w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-78-300x123.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-78-510x210.jpg 510w" sizes="(max-width: 545px) 100vw, 545px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-415249" class="wp-caption-text">Enable Mobile and logged in users cache</p></div>\n<p><b>Preload options</b></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">You can further optimize your caching with scheduled preloader options. This features works by allowing the user to preload the pages of the site, further improving its performance. When combined with the other caching features within WP-Optimize, the preloader is a powerful tool that can help speed up loading times.¬†¬†¬†</span></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-74.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-415233 aligncenter" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-74.jpg" alt="" width="618" height="420" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-74.jpg 618w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-74-300x204.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-74-510x347.jpg 510w" sizes="(max-width: 618px) 100vw, 618px" /></a></p>\n<p><b>Advanced settings</b></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In the ‚ÄúAdvanced settings‚Äù tab, you can add any URLs, cookies and user agent strings you would like excluded from the cache. These options can be a great tool and very useful as they allow you to exclude sensitive site pages from the caching engine, such as login URLs.</span></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-75.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-415234 aligncenter" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-75.jpg" alt="" width="583" height="657" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-75.jpg 583w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-75-266x300.jpg 266w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-75-510x575.jpg 510w" sizes="(max-width: 583px) 100vw, 583px" /></a></p>\n<p><b>G-Zip compression</b></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This option can give a huge percentage boost as part of your total savings and is a simple and effective way to save bandwidth and further speed up your site. G-Zip compression reduces the size of files sent from your server to increase the speed to which they are transferred to the users browser. Just click ‚Äúenable‚Äù to activate this option.¬†¬†</span></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-76.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-415237 aligncenter" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-76.jpg" alt="" width="621" height="224" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-76.jpg 621w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-76-300x108.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-76-510x184.jpg 510w" sizes="(max-width: 621px) 100vw, 621px" /></a></p>\n<p><b>Static file caching</b></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Finally, ‚ÄúStatic file caching‚Äù lets you use HTTP response headers. Once enabled, a visitor&#8217;s browser will know if it should cache non-changing files, so it does not need to retrieve them upon every visit, further improving the loading speed of your site. Just set your expiration time and press ‚Äúenable‚Äù to activate.</span></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-77.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-415240 aligncenter" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-77.jpg" alt="" width="622" height="238" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-77.jpg 622w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-77-300x115.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/New-Project-77-510x195.jpg 510w" sizes="(max-width: 622px) 100vw, 622px" /></a></p>\n<p><b>WP-Optimize in summary</b></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The caching feature is the latest in a series of site optimization options that aim to make WP-Optimize your one stop shop for improving your sites speed and performance. Along with image optimization and database cleaning, the addition of caching aims to make WP-Optimize the only WordPress optimization tool you need.¬†</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To find out how to use all the WP-Optimize features, please follow the links for further information on </span><a href="https://vimeo.com/user48800063/download/339511213/c742ac09e2"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Database Cleaning</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> and </span><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-release-new-how-to-video-for-image-optimization/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Image Optimization</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">.¬†</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To find out more about WP-Optimize, visit the </span><a href="https://getwpo.com/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">website</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> today.</span></p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-expands-to-a-market-leading-3-in-1-optimization-plugin-with-new-caching-feature/">WP-Optimize expands to a market leading 3-in-1 optimization plugin with new caching feature</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href="http://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:121:"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-expands-to-a-market-leading-3-in-1-optimization-plugin-with-new-caching-feature/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:116:"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-expands-to-a-market-leading-3-in-1-optimization-plugin-with-new-caching-feature/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:67:"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:72:"UpdraftPlus release new update: Includes new empty clone install feature";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:58:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/cUygmIgZkuc/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:104:"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-new-update-includes-new-empty-clone-install-feature/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 24 Jul 2019 11:02:16 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:28:"UpdraftPlus development news";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:24:"updraft plus development";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"UpdraftPlus";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:33:"https://updraftplus.com/?p=414869";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:816:"<p>UpdraftPlus have now released the latest update for all our users which includes a host of features, fixes and tweak updates. As mentioned in our previous blog, this latest update includes a new feature that allows users who want to &#8230; <a href="https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-new-update-includes-new-empty-clone-install-feature/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-new-update-includes-new-empty-clone-install-feature/">UpdraftPlus release new update: Includes new empty clone install feature</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href="http://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"wmullins";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5086:"<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">UpdraftPlus have now released the latest update for all our users which includes a host of features, fixes and tweak updates. As mentioned in our </span><a href="https://updraftplus.com/updraftclone-gets-a-new-dashboard-update/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">previous blog</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, this latest update includes a new feature that allows users who want to create a new clone site to use an already existing local backup (one that is not in remote storage) to create one via </span><a href="https://updraftplus.com/updraftclone/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">UpdraftClone</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This allows the whole clone creation process to be set up in a much shorter amount of time as it is not necessary to create a new backup of the site you are cloning first. This amazing new feature will still use the existing Clone token system that everyone is familiar with, so users can begin generating new blank WordPress installs straight away, without having to purchase any additional services. Once you are done with the testing of the clone, you can simply delete it and generate another one as and when it is needed.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The changelog for UpdraftPlus Free (1.16.16) and UpdraftPlus Premium (2.16.16) is as follows.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We recommend the update for all users.</span></p>\n<p><b>1.16.16 ‚Äì 2.16.16</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">FEATURE: Added the ability to launch a blank WordPress clone</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">FEATURE: Add ‚Äìcollate= parameter to WP-CLI (Premium) to allow substitution of locally unknown collations when restoring</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">FIX: Switched to wp_insert_site() from insert_blog() and install_blog() method when importing single-site into a multisite network on WP 5.1+. Fixes ‚ÄòAlready Installed‚Äô error when importing on newer WP versions</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">FIX: Issue where (rare) foreign key constraints aren‚Äôt updated upon restore when table prefix changes</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">FIX: Improve parsing of backed-up triggers when restoring preventing possible unnecessary errors</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">FIX: If an upload to Google Drive starts to fail due to an OAuth token refresh error, the backup will re-bootstrap the Drive client and try again</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">FIX: JSON-reparser to prevent unwanted RINFO data being output to screen</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">FIX: Triggers were still included in a backup for tables that were excluded because of lack of WP prefix</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">FIX: Resuming restores could resume at an unnecessarily early stage</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">FIX: Issue with Dropbox account information call that could make it fail</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">TWEAK: In cases where there were duplicate Google Drive folders (which is possible if there are multiple network communications failures when looking up the folder), these are now detected and merged automatically</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">TWEAK: Add option to start 250GB Vault subscription as in-app purchase</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">TWEAK: Regression: backup checksums were not being recorded in the backup log file</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">TWEAK: Remove UpdraftClone when the backup is cancelled by the user</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">TWEAK: Send the backup log during the creation of UpdraftClone for easier support when a clone fails to recieve the backup</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">TWEAK: Detect OneDrive Graph token expiries and initiate swift resumption</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">TWEAK: Reduce the permissions requested for the UpdraftPlus Google Drive app (this now means that backups manually uploaded to Google Drive can not be deleted through the UpdraftPlus UI)</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-new-update-includes-new-empty-clone-install-feature/">UpdraftPlus release new update: Includes new empty clone install feature</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href="http://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:101:"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-new-update-includes-new-empty-clone-install-feature/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:96:"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-new-update-includes-new